contentrichtext.text: '''Gregory III''' may refer to: * [[Pope Gregory III]], in office 731–741 * [[Gregory III, Count of Tusculum]], r. 1058-1108 * [[Grigor III Pahlavuni]], Armenian Catholicos of Cilicia in 1113–1166 * [[Gregory III Šubić of Bribir]], died in 1342 or 1356, Croatian noble * [[Patriarch Gregory III of Alexandria]], Greek Orthodox patriarch, in office 1354-1366 * [[Patriarch Gregory III of Constantinople]], in office 1443-1450 * [[Gregory III Laham]], Patriarch of the Melkite Greek Catholic Church from 2000 {{hndis}}
